ure and work alongside other social media marketing tactics like organic posting and audience engagement. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/social-media-marketing\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"social-media-advertising-101\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/07\/18\/social-media-advertising\">Social media advertising 101<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>New to running ads on social media? This is a great place to start. You\u2019ll learn about the different social platforms, see how social ads work, and understand the costs associated with this advertising channel. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/07\/18\/social-media-advertising\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"why-advertise-on-social-media\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/02\/02\/reasons-to-advertise-on-social-media\">Why advertise on social media?<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>You probably have an inkling as to why investing in social ads is a good idea. This guide tells the whole story\u2014from social ads\u2019 low entry cost to the creative freedom they encourage. Read up on all the benefits of social media advertising to get a feel for what they can do for your business. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/02\/02\/reasons-to-advertise-on-social-media\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"social-media-advertising-tips\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2016\/06\/30\/social-media-advertising-tips\">Social media advertising tips<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>You know why social media ads are beneficial and how they work. Let\u2019s level up those ad campaigns with 10 tactical tips to get more reach and lower the costs of each click, lead, and conversion. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2016\/06\/30\/social-media-advertising-tips\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"facebook-advertising\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/05\/03\/how-to-advertise-on-facebook\">Facebook advertising<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>Facebook remains the 800-pound social media gorilla with more active monthly users than any other platform (it also delivers some of the lowest costs-per-click in the biz). Read this guide to learn how to open your Facebook ad account, set up ad tracking, and create your first ad campaign so you can engage this massive audience. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/05\/03\/how-to-advertise-on-facebook\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"instagram-advertising\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/instagram-advertising\">Instagram advertising<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>Instagram continues to add new ad formats that let creative marketers reach customers in exciting ways. This complete guide provides the lowdown on Instagram ads. You\u2019ll learn how to choose marketing objectives, configure audience targeting, set campaign budgets, and a whole lot more. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/instagram-advertising\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"tiktok-advertising\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2020\/07\/22\/tiktok-ads\">TikTok advertising<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>TikTok is now where people of all generations go to be entertained and educated. It\u2019s even becoming a search engine of sorts, with users perusing posts to learn about new products and brands. This five-step starter guide to TikTok ads will help you connect with this audience of curious consumers. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2020\/07\/22\/tiktok-ads\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"linkedin-advertising\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/03\/05\/linkedin-advertising\">LinkedIn advertising<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>LinkedIn is the epicenter of business-to-business networking. If you sell to other businesses or to the people who run them, LinkedIn ads should be a top contender for your ad dollars. Here, you\u2019ll see what ad types are available on LinkedIn, learn how to target specific audiences, and get tips to net the best return on each ad dollar you spend. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/03\/05\/linkedin-advertising\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"youtube-advertising\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2017\/02\/23\/youtube-advertising-tips\">YouTube advertising<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>Millions of people watch billions of videos on YouTube every day. From the basics to the advanced, this guide covers everything you need to launch an ad campaign on YouTube that matches your brand and goals. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2017\/02\/23\/youtube-advertising-tips\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"snapchat-advertising\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/01\/09\/snapchat-ads\">Snapchat advertising<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>Snapchat is popular with 18 to 24-year-olds. If your target audience skews toward young adults, this guide is for you. In it, you\u2019ll learn how to leverage several ad features, such as Collection Ads, AR filters, and Story Ads. Plus, you\u2019ll get a lesson on Snapchat analytics that\u2019ll help you make every ad more relevant to each audience segment. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/01\/09\/snapchat-ads\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"social-shopping\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/04\/25\/social-shopping\">Social shopping for beginners<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>Social shopping, aka social commerce, is all about helping social media scrollers discover and purchase products with as little friction as possible (and without leaving their favorite social media app). This guide walks you through the basics of social shopping ad campaigns on popular platforms and gives pointers for creating irresistible ads. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/04\/25\/social-shopping\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"social-media-ad-metrics\"><\/div>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2018\/12\/05\/social-media-metrics\">Social media ad metrics<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>No matter which platforms you choose, it\u2019s critical that you understand which tactics and targets bring the sales and which burn through your ad budget. This list of the most important social media ad metrics shows you how to measure each one and use them to make every campaign more profitable than the last. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2018\/12\/05\/social-media-metrics\">Read more &gt;&gt;<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn everything you need to successfully run social ads campaigns on major social media platforms.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":263,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"_et_pb_use_builder":"","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false},"class_list":["post-83928","learn","type-learn","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Social Ads 101 | WordStream<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Learn how to create, manage, and optimize social ads for major social media platforms in a series of lessons from beginner to advanced.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/social-ads-101\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Social Ads 101 | WordStream\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Learn how to create, manage, and optimize social ads for major social media platforms in a series of lessons from 